01:55.000 --> 02:17.000
The bill which passed the both houses of Congress and the Senate to the President provided for the establishment of an agency with $250,000 to try to retrain people in areas where their industries have moved away and coal mining areas where the coal has been exhausted and the people are just living there.

02:17.000 --> 02:30.000
